products.title: Asus Zenbook pro
products.discription: Whether it's working on a presentation, streaming movies and music, or playing games, the Asus ZenBook Pro 15 is your ideal companion for work or play. Featuring an awe-inspiring design, the NanoEdge 4K UHD Ultraslim-bezel Display, an 8th Generation Intel Core i9 hexa-core processor, and a powerful Li-ion battery, this laptop brings to you the best of both worlds in terms of style and performance.

products.title: Sony PlayStation 5
products.discription: Experience lightning-fast loading with an ultra-high speed SSD, deeper immersion with support for haptic feedback1, adaptive triggers1 and 3D Audio*, and an all-new generation of incredible PlayStation games.

products.title: Apple iPhone 14 Pro
products.discription: The iPhone 14 Pro represents a duality, both as something  extremely similar to its predecessor while also being simultaneously new. It features a lot of camera upgrades and the Dynamic Island, which replaces the infamous notch five years after the notch’s debut on the iPhone X.

products.title: Sony WH-1000XM5 headphones
products.discription: Industry Leading noise cancellation-two processors control 8 microphones for unprecedented noise cancellation. With Auto NC Optimizer, noise cancelling is automatically optimized based on your wearing conditions and environment.

products.title: Samsung 4k smart tv
products.discription: Indulge yourself in a world of infinite visual entertainment with the one-of-a-kind Samsung TV, which is packed with captivating features and will take your breath away with its remarkable performance. This TV offers a brilliant colour-enriched picture that brings out the best in every piece of material it displays, providing a fantastic viewing experience. Furthermore, when put in the living room, this TV attracts all of the attention it deserves because of its sleek, modern, and fantastic appearance. Furthermore, the Auto Low Latency Mode on this TV optimises your screen so you have better flexibility with decreased input lag.

products.title: Sofa

products.title: LG washing machine
products.discription: Using the LG FHM1207SDL 7 kg Fully Automatic Front-loading Washing Machine makes washing clothing quick and easy. It features Allergy Care that eliminates the majority of viruses and ensures a sanitary wash each time. Also, the motor is directly attached to the drum, which eliminates the need for a pulley or belt, decreasing energy wastage, vibrations and noise. Furthermore, the 6 Motion DD technology optimises the washing motion according to the fabric type.

products.discription: The Wakeup Pluto Wood Bed is comfortable and roomy. This traditional piece of furniture has plenty of storage space, making it the ideal bed for you. Its modern yet traditional wooden attire will fill the place with scenic beauty.

products.title: Asics men shoes
products.discription: The dynablast running shoe comfortably locks the shoe around the foot like a gentle hug. This design means there are fewer layers of material, resulting in a light, breathable upper. The upper, combined with a responsive underfoot ride, makes this new dynablast style feel springy and energetic. It is recommend for runners who want a fun underfoot experience in their training.
